1
00:00:10,279 --> 00:00:10,880
Dr. Xu

2
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:12,919
What are the preliminary findings?

3
00:00:13,039 --> 00:00:14,839
Based on the victim's physical features,

4
00:00:15,119 --> 00:00:15,880
the preliminary estimate is

5
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:18,079
the victim died about three to four days ago.

6
00:00:18,359 --> 00:00:18,839
Scissors.

7
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:54,600
We found Zhao Yan's body

8
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,039
inside Lele's home.

9
00:00:56,799 --> 00:00:57,960
But she refuses to say anything.

10
00:00:58,759 --> 00:00:59,520
From what we know,

11
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,079
she has no real family or friends.

12
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,159
The person she trusts most

13
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:05,040
is you.

14
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,200
You want me to persuade Lele?

15
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:10,400
No way.

16
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:12,680
She can't be the criminal.

17
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,599
She's a kind person.

18
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,000
Let me tell you,

19
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,680
even with zero confession,

20
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,920
as long as the chain of evidence is complete,

21
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,120
we can still convict her.

22
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,120
Mao Lele.

23
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,920
Still refusing to say anything, huh?

24
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:24,159
But we hope she'll come clean voluntarily

25
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,439
to earn leniency.

26
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,439
We're giving her a chance.

27
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:31,799
Hold on.

28
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:33,319
An old friend's come to see you.

29
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,040
Look at you.

30
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,680
Haven't been eating properly again, huh?

31
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,000
You've gotten so thin.

32
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,920
There's no point in living.

33
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,480
How many times have I told you?

34
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,840
No more negative talk.

35
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,400
You need to pull yourself together.

36
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,280
Don't let people think we're easy to bully.

37
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:08,960
Brother.

38
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:11,360
Don't be so good to me.

39
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,360
I don't deserve it.

40
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,400
I'm the one who let you down.

41
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,879
I didn't protect you well enough.

42
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,280
Listen to me.

43
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,800
Let's tell them everything we know.

44
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,719
You'll feel better once you do.

45
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,000
Tianfang.

46
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:28,759
You always loved telling the story of the Massacre of the Bai family.

47
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,280
I just want to ask you,

48
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,840
Bai the Second killed Elder Bai's whole family.

49
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,599
Was it because

50
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,680
he couldn't have the woman he loved,

51
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,120
so he destroyed everything?

52
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:43,360
The human heart is complicated.

53
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,360
Maybe

54
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,879
Bai the Second was just jealous of Elder Bai.

55
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:47,960
Even if his brother

56
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,879
hadn't married the woman he loved,

57
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,000
he would've struck for some other reason.

58
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,960
Then I guess I did it out of jealousy too.

59
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,439
I envied those pretty girls

60
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,319
who, just because of their faces,

61
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,439
could get away with anything.

62
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,319
The body was found in my place,

63
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:12,039
but that doesn't prove I killed anyone.

64
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:14,759
I heard Captain Chu once bullied Tianfang.

65
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,960
I have just one request.

66
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,759
If you can find

67
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,120
evidence that I committed murder,

68
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,840
I'll tell you everything.

69
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,000
Tweezers.

70
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,000
Found it at last.

71
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,040
Mao Lele.

72
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,279
On the gauze that wrapped Zhao Yan,

73
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,439
we found an eyelash.

74
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,199
After DNA comparison,

75
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,040
it's yours.

76
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:37,920
Anything you'd like to say?

77
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,000
I really shouldn't have shed tears for him.

78
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:41,800
I killed him.

79
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,319
No one else was involved.

80
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:45,199
Then why did you kill Cindy?

81
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:48,759
I didn't kill her.

82
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,759
Cindy.

83
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,000
Look at these two.

84
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,759
Which one's prettier?

85
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,399
From the moment I was born,

86
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,439
I had a huge birthmark.

87
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,680
Everyone despised me.

88
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:02,240
Facial skin is less than 0.5 millimeters thick,

89
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:04,560
yet it dictates a person's whole life.

90
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,800
Some are showered with endless love,

91
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,000
while others...

92
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,839
are scorned their entire lives.

93
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,600
How ironic.

94
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:13,079
Lele, come here.

95
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,519
Paint my nails.

96
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,800
I won't make you do it for free.

97
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,120
This much money

98
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,600
should feed you for a month, right?

99
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,800
Paint my nails.

100
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,279
Stand right there.

101
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,759
We kindly offer you a job,

102
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,759
and you're not even grateful?

103
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,439
Are you going or not?

104
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,279
No.

105
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:49,959
Are you going or not?

106
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:52,079
Ugly freaks just love acting up.

107
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,800
Let me go!

108
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:54,759
Let me go!

109
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,639
If you keep this up, I'll...

110
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,839
I'll tell Manager Yu.

111
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,480
Go ahead, try telling him.

112
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,920
We'll deal with him too.

113
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,800
Tell who?

114
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,560
I asked, tell who?

115
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:09,439
Speak up!

116
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,040
Don't touch me!

117
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,360
Why aren't you talking now?

118
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,480
Let me go!

119
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,319
Tell who?

120
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,199
Get up, now!

121
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:20,839
Let me go!

122
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,120
Stand up!

123
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,759
Get up!

124
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,560
Get up!

125
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,319
Then why didn't you tell Yu Tianfang?

126
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,519
She didn't want the person she loved

127
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:46,839
to see her at her most pathetic.

128
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,000
What do you mean?

129
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,319
When you love someone,

130
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,680
you only want to show them your best side.

131
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:54,920
Yu Tianfang,

132
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,759
how clueless can you be?

133
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,920
She liked me.

134
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:04,079
She cared about you too much,

135
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,759
that's why she didn't tell you the truth.

136
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:06,759
And in the end,

137
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,160
she got deceived by Zhao Yan again.

138
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,240
No way.

139
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,240
She really liked me?

140
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,639
Zhao Yan really is a bastard.

141
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,680
You're pretty much a bastard too.

142
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:24,240
What's your relationship with Zhao Yan?

143
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:28,920
I once thought

144
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,560
that besides Tianfang,

145
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,439
he was the only one who treated me best.

146
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,439
Pretty little thing, aren't you?

147
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,279
Give me a kiss.

148
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:48,720
Let go!

149
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,560
I've got plenty of money.

150
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:52,040
That's all you want, isn't it?

151
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,560
What are you doing?

152
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,040
Who the hell are you?

153
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,920
Let me tell you something.

154
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,959
If you dare bully this girl again,

155
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,439
I'll break your legs.

156
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,199
I won't do it again!

157
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:04,759
Get lost!

158
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:05,519
I won't do it again!

159
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:06,759
Manager Zhao,

160
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,199
thank you so much for today.

161
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,319
You offended a client to save me,

162
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,319
and got fined by the company.

163
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,560
I don't know how to repay you.

164
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,600
Don't mention it.

165
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,360
We're all colleagues here.

166
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,720
If you really want to thank me,

167
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,160
bottoms up.

168
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:24,360
I usually don't drink,

169
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,480
but today, to thank you, Manager Zhao,

170
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,839
I'll have one with you.

171
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,399
Alright.

172
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,120
Have another one.

173
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,600
She's got some looks, huh.

174
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,240
What have you done?

175
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,759
Lele, listen to me.

176
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,559
I truly love you.

177
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,000
I'll take responsibility for you.

178
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,000
There are so many beauties at the resort.

179
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,559
Why did you have to deceive me?

180
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,879
How could I be deceiving you?

181
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,440
You're different from them.

182
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,720
I love that pure quality about you.

183
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:51,759
I don't believe you.

184
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:52,240
Lele.

185
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,159
Listen to me. Get away from me!

186
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,440
Lele, Lele, listen to me.

187
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,320
Lele.

188
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,720
I think you're a gift

189
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,480
that heaven sent to me.

190
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,720
Give me time.

191
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,279
I'll prove it to you.

192
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,759
Lele.

193
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,759
This is my gift to you.

194
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,200
I tattooed your name on my body.

195
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,519
I'll never forget you.

196
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:17,879
Will you love me forever?

197
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,080
Once I've saved up enough money,

198
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,639
I'll propose to you.

199
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,399
Thank you, Manager Zhao.

200
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,240
Still calling me Manager Zhao?

201
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,440
Call me Yan.

202
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:26,879
Thank you, Yan.

203
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,039
That's more like it.

204
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:29,960
Order whatever you want.

205
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,559
Don't try to save money for me.

206
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,960
But we shouldn't waste either.

207
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,759
Don't try to save money for me.

208
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,320
Order.

209
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,320
Then...

210
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,080
let's get an order of malatang.

211
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:38,879
Okay.

212
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:39,919
Waiter!

213
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,480
We'll have

214
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,080
one order

215
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,840
of malatang for three yuan.

216
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,240
Three yuan of malatang?

217
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,080
Three yuan.

218
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,080
You can mix it however you like.

219
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:53,559
Delicious.

220
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,799
He got a tattoo for me

221
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,960
and said he'd marry me.

222
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,399
I thought it was true love.

223
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,480
I truly carved him onto my body.

224
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:06,399
But it was all a lie.

225
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,320
I won the bet last time.

226
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,759
I scored Lele.

227
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,639
I don't believe it.

228
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:16,519
Stop trying to weasel out of paying.

229
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,200
Don't believe me, huh?

230
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:21,720
Take a look at this.

231
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:24,480
Squeezed her dry.

232
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:26,080
And she's even grateful for it,

233
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,679
got my name tattooed on her.

234
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,720
You're really wicked.

235
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,600
Just slapped on a tattoo sticker

236
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,120
and tricked her into giving herself to you.

237
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:37,000
She did more than give herself to me.

238
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,399
She handed over this month's salary too.

239
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:41,879
We agreed, right?

240
00:11:42,919 --> 00:11:44,879
The kitchen kickbacks this month

241
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,559
all go to me.

242
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:47,799
Fine.

243
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,799
I'll let you off this month.

244
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:50,960
But next month,

245
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,200
we split it evenly.

246
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,320
If I really become general manager,

247
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,240
would I shortchange you two?

248
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:01,200
It's that suck-up Yu Tianfang.

249
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,799
He's always hovering around Boss Bai.

250
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,120
We've got to find a way to get rid of him.

251
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:05,759
Don't worry.

252
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,679
We've got it all planned.

253
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,840
We'll use a honey trap.

254
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,799
Take nude photos of him.

255
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:17,159
Beautiful.

256
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,200
Let's do it.

257
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,720
Going against me?

258
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,240
Think he'll meet a good end?

259
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,440
Know why I brought you here?

260
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,960
Based on our forensics team's analysis

261
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,720
and the evidence found here,

262
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,679
the spot where Cindy fell in

263
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,399
was within 100 meters of this place.

264
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,960
Right before Cindy died,

265
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:52,279
she was lying right here.

266
00:12:53,279 --> 00:12:54,840
That day, I just wanted to ask her

267
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,720
why she kept targeting me.

268
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:57,799
Boss,

269
00:12:58,279 --> 00:13:00,039
why is the anesthetic I ordered short?

270
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,240
I'm giving my friend Botox to fill in scars.

271
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,240
Of course I need extra for local anesthesia.

272
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:10,240
Fine, fine, I don't care.

273
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,799
You have to make up the amount.

274
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,039
Or I'll report you.

275
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,720
I wonder how well it works.

276
00:13:24,919 --> 00:13:26,879
If only I had someone to practice on.

277
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:30,240
Cindy,

278
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,200
why did you team up

279
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,840
with Zhao Yan to deceive me?

280
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,799
I felt someone was watching me.

281
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,679
Turns out it's you, you ugly freak.

282
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,519
Why did you lie to me?

283
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,799
Me, lie to you?

284
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:46,639
Looking like you do,

285
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,600
what man would ever want you?

286
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:50,039
I had Zhao Yan chase you.

287
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,799
